author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
This week, we’ll speak with Marvel Studios’ The Fantastic Four: First Steps director Matt Shakman about his work on the film. Then, Marvel Comics Vice President and Executive Editor Tom Brevoort discusses Fantastic Four: First Steps issue #1. Later on, we’ll hear from physicist David Smith about the real-world science of invisibility. 

00:00 - Welcome Back!
1:09 - Director Matt Shakman on his work in Marvel Studios’ The Fantastic Four: First Steps
12:50 - Marvel Comics Vice President and Executive Editor Tom Brevoort discusses Fantastic Four: First Steps issue #1 
20:08 - Physicist David Smith on IRL invisibility
